  "data": {
    "title": "Close CRM Tips: Best Ways to Sell Faster in 2025",
    "excerpt": "Discover the best ways to use Close CRM for inside sales. Built-in calling, SMS, automation, and Chloe AI agent. Start your free trial today.",
    "featured_image": {
      "$media": {
        "url": "https://tonyciencia.com/blog/close-tips.jpg",
        "alt": "Close CRM Tips: Best Ways to Sell Faster in 2025",
        "filename": "close-tips.jpg"
      }
    },
    "content": [
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l0",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/what-is-close"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If your sales team lives on the phone, sends dozens of follow-up texts a day, and relies on repeatable outreach sequences to hit quota — you need a CRM that was actually built for that workflow. Not a generic project manager with a contacts tab bolted on. That's where ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Close",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " shines.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Close is a CRM designed from the ground up for inside sales teams. It bundles calling, email, SMS, pipeline management, and automation into one clean interface. And now, with Chloe — an AI sales agent that calls and qualifies leads the moment they come in — Close is doing something almost no other CRM in its price range offers.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I've spent serious time exploring what makes Close different. Below are my best tips and ways to get the most out of it — whether you're a solo closer or scaling a team of thirty.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "*Disclosure: Some links below are affiliate links. If you sign up through them, I may earn a commission at no extra cost to you.*",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Start with the Built-In Calling (Seriously, Use It)",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The single biggest mistake new Close users make? They sign up and immediately plug in a third-party dialer. Don't do that.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Close has native calling baked into every plan — including the $9/month Solo tier. You get a local phone number, automatic call logging, call recording, and the ability to make and receive calls without ever leaving the CRM. No Twilio integration headaches. No Zapier workarounds.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Here's what that looks like in practice: a lead fills out your web form. Close captures it. You click the lead, hit the call button, and you're talking in under ten seconds. The call gets logged automatically. If you leave a voicemail, you can drop a pre-recorded message in one click.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "For teams doing high-volume outreach, this alone saves hours per week. And since Close has handled over ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "2 billion calls, emails, and texts",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ", the infrastructure is battle-tested.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Let Chloe Qualify Leads Before Your Team Even Sees Them",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This is Close's most exciting feature right now, and it deserves its own section.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Chloe is an AI sales agent that lives inside your Close account. When a new lead arrives, Chloe can call them automatically — no human involved — have a real conversation, ask qualifying questions, and even book a meeting on your rep's calendar. All while updating the CRM record with notes and status changes.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Think about what that means for response time. Most sales teams take 30+ minutes to respond to an inbound lead. Chloe responds in seconds. And response speed is one of the strongest predictors of conversion.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Every Close plan includes AI credits (500/month on Solo, scaling up on higher tiers). You don't need a separate AI platform or a developer to set it up. Chloe is part of the CRM — toggle it on, configure your qualifying criteria, and let it work.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l1",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/how-to-use-close"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you want to learn exactly how to configure Chloe and get the best results, check out our ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "step-by-step Close tutorial",
            "marks": [
              "l1"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ".",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Build Sequences That Do the Follow-Up for You",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Follow-up is where most deals are won or lost. And most reps are terrible at it — not because they're lazy, but because they're juggling 50 active leads and things slip through the cracks.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Close solves this with automated sequences (they call them \"Workflows\"). You can build multi-step sequences that mix emails, calls, and SMS messages on a schedule you define. A typical sequence might look like:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Day 1:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Automated email introducing your product",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Day 2:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Task reminder to call the lead",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Day 4:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " SMS follow-up with a short question",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Day 7:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Another email with a case study",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Day 10:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Final call attempt with a voicemail drop",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Once a lead replies or books a meeting, the sequence stops automatically. No awkward double-texts. No wasted calls to people who already said yes.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The SMS integration is particularly powerful. You can send and receive texts right inside Close — the same way you handle email. For sales teams targeting prospects who prefer texting over email, this is a game-changer.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Use the Pipeline View to Stay Focused on What Matters",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Close's pipeline view is visual, drag-and-drop, and fast. You can see exactly where every deal sits, filter by rep, stage, value, or date, and move deals forward with a single click.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "A few tips to get the most out of it:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Create multiple pipelines",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " if you sell different products or have separate new-business and renewal flows. Close lets you run as many as you need.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Set up Smart Views",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " to save custom filters. For example: \"All deals over $5K in the demo stage assigned to me\" — saved in one click, accessible forever.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Use the Activities view",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " to see what happened today across your whole team. Calls made, emails sent, meetings booked — all in one timeline.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "For teams that have outgrown spreadsheets but don't need the complexity of Salesforce, Close hits a sweet spot. It's powerful enough to run a serious sales operation, but your reps won't need a week of training to figure it out.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
