            "text": "Shared Credit Pools (Essentials & Growth):",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Teams can pool AI credits across users, with caps that scale as your team grows. This makes it easy to allocate AI power where it matters most.",
