          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What makes Close CRM different from other CRMs?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Close was built specifically for inside sales teams. Unlike general-purpose CRMs, it includes native calling, SMS, and email in every plan — no integrations needed. Plus, Chloe, its built-in AI sales agent, can call and qualify leads automatically the moment they enter your pipeline.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "How much does Close CRM cost?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Close starts at $9/month per user on the Solo plan (paid annually). The Essentials plan is $35/month per user, and the Growth plan is $99/month per user. All plans include AI credits, built-in calling, and a free trial with no credit card required.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Can Close CRM handle both phone calls and text messages?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes. Close has native calling and SMS built into every plan. You can make and receive calls, drop pre-recorded voicemails, and send/receive texts — all from inside the CRM. No third-party dialer or messaging app required.",
